<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8f176513-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s1645j"><num value="1645j">§ 1645j.</num><heading> Settlement period</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Commission shall complete its affairs in connection with the settlement of claims pursuant to this subchapter not later than three years after the final date for the filing of claims as provided in <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s1645b">section 1645b of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id8f176514-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/act/1950-03-10/ch54">Mar. 10, 1950, ch. 54</ref>, title VII, § 711, as added <ref href="/us/pl/96/606">Pub. L. 96–606</ref>, <date date="1980-12-28">Dec. 28, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/3537">94 Stat. 3537</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
